        <title>UV Leak Detection Kit</title>
        <figure id="f2700831" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figh31/H31417.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>ZTSE4618</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>The UV leak detection kit is used with fuel dye to quickly identify leaks. The fuel dye combines with fuel
            and migrates out at the leak. The ultraviolet lamp illuminates the leaking fuel dye, which appears
            fluorescent yellow-green in color.
        </para>
